import React from 'react'
import { Drawer , List, ListItemButton, ListItemIcon, ListItemText ,Button } from '@mui/material'

export const DrawerComp = () => {
  return (
    <React.Fragment>
      <Drawer open={true}>
         <List>
            <ListItemButton>
                <ListItemIcon>
                    <ListItemText>
                    <Button sx={{marginLeft:"auto" ,  }} variant='contained' >
                  Login{""}
                </Button>
                    </ListItemText>
                </ListItemIcon>
            </ListItemButton>
         </List>
      </Drawer>
    </React.Fragment>
  )
  }
  export default DrawerComp;
